# campus.mojo - Cursor Rules

> **Globale Standards:** `/root/projects/CODING_STANDARDS.md`

## Projekt-Info

- **Typ:** Learning Management System (LMS)
- **Domain:** campus.mojo-institut.de
- **Stack:** Next.js + Fastify + Prisma

## Architektur

```
packages/
├── web/        # Frontend (Next.js)
└── api/        # Backend API (Fastify)
```

## Wichtige Patterns

1. **Multitenancy:** `@mojo/tenant` Middleware (Creator können eigene Kurse hosten)
2. **Auth:** Clerk JWT
3. **Entitlements:** User-Berechtigungen für Kurse via `EntitlementGate`
